## ğŸ“œ Licensing Model

This project operates under a **dual-license model** to balance intellectual property protection with open collaboration.

-   **Proprietary Core IP**: Our physical product formulations, manufacturing processes, and core business strategies are confidential and protected. See **[LICENSE-PROPRIETARY.md](LICENSE-PROPRIETARY.md)**.
-   **Open Digital Platform**: The source code for our digital platforms and our educational content are licensed under a permissive open-source license (e.g., MIT or CC BY-NC-SA 4.0) to encourage community contribution. See **[LICENSE-OPEN.md](LICENSE-OPEN.md)**.

Please refer to the specific license files for detailed terms.

